      "description": "Solid budget-minded driver/project with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. Runs, drives, and presents as an honest used car with visible cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the powertrain feels serviceable and the chassis remains composed. Recent maintenance attention helps it start up reliably and get down the road without drama. Great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation, a shop car, or a platform to sort and improve over time. Priced fairly for the condition and value here.",
